title: Fundraising Art Sale Ends Thursday (Minnesota State University – Moorhead)
text: ( Source : Minnesota State University – Moorhead ) The faculty donated art sale at the Roland Dille Center for the Arts Gallery ends this Thursday, October 22 at 9pm. The art sale is part of the larger faculty exhibition ' Rainbows / Doom '.
